events.text:
Day Magenta
I’ve lost count of how long I’ve been here, so the numbers don’t seem to matter anymore.
Today feels like a magenta.
I wonder what came first – the moon bunny or the moon carrots?
Did they grow alone on this dusty rock?
Did the moon bunny ever have any natural predators?
I’ve only seen the one in the base.
How did it get in there?
What did it do before I came along?
Does it really need me to collect carrots for it?
Am I but a vessel, a minion of the moon bunny?
Who is really in charge of this moon?
If it came to a fight, could I take the moon bunny?
I have no answers to these questions.
All I know is that the moon bunny and I need something to eat for dinner, and it doesn’t seem keen on helping.
